.subPage.hostgator.animated
  .subHeader.container-fluid
    .row
      .col-sm-3
        %a{:href => "/portfolio"} < back

      .col-sm-6.text-center
        %span.title Hostgator

      .col-sm-3


  .subPageContent.container
    .row
      .col-xs-12.logoWrp.text-center
        %img.img-responsive{:src => "../images/hostgator-logo.png"}


    .row
      .col-sm-12.introWrp
        .titleWrp.text-center
          %p.title
            %span Overview

        %p.para.text-justify
          Hostgator is a leading US based hosting company. My role involved replicating the styling and theme from Hostgator.com website to the .IN site and integrating it into the in house CMS, Supersite
          %a{:href => "http://manage.hostgator.in/kb/servlet/KBServlet/faq783.html", :target => "_blank", :title => "What is Supersite"} (?)
          \. The .CN (China) and MY (Malaysian) versions of the site where also build, styled and themed as designed and then integrated into the CMS, Supersite. My Role also involved maintenance and management of the site, including making bug-fixes, debugging and making promotional changes to the site from time to time.

        %p.btnWrp.text-center
          %a.btn.btn-success.checkInAction{:href => "http://www.hostgator.in", :target => "_blank", :rel => "nofollow"} Checkout the site


        .infoWrp.row
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.roleWrp
            %p.title My Role:
            %p.role
              HTML / HTML5, CSS / CSS3, Bootstrap, Javascript, Jquery, Backbone

          .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.platformWrp
            %p.title Platforms:
            %ul.platforms
              %li.pull-left.fa.fa-desktop.active
              %li.pull-left.fa.fa-tablet.active
              %li.pull-left.fa.fa-mobile.active

    .row
      .col-sm-12.snapshotWrp
        .titleWrp.text-center
          %p.title
            %span Snapshots

        .snapshots
          .row-fluid
            %img.img-responsive{:src => "../images/responsive-showcase-hostgator.jpg"}
